-- X5 Discount Unit Chief Vysotsky Quits Russia’s Largest Retailer
-- B y   I l y a   K h r e n n i k o v
-- 2012-03-05T07:04:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-05/vysotsky-head-of-x5-s-pyaterochka-unit-quits-vedomosti-says.html
X5 Retail Group,  Russia ’s largest
food retailer by sales, said the head of its discount format
division quit after 15 years with the company.  Oleg Vysotsky will continue to manage the division until a
replacement is found and will then serve as a transition
adviser, X5 said in a statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
